c: 4
v: 167
t: "Zvirokwazvo, avo vasingatendi (nekuviga chokwadi pamusoro pamutumwa Muhammad (SAW) nemashoko ake echokwadi echitendero cheIslaam sezvakanyorwa muTorah (Taurah) uye muInjeel (Vhangeri)) uye vakadzivirira vanhu kubva munzira yaAllah (Islaam); nokudaro zvirokwazvo vanhu vakarasika zvikuru"